June 6 (Reuters) -  U.S. stock index e-mini futures slightly higher on Friday: Dow Jones industrial average futures <1YMc1> were up 0.16 percent at 16,845, S&P 500 futures <ESc1> were up 0.06 percent at 1,939.75 and Nasdaq 100 futures <NQc1> were up 0.08 percent at 3,779.25. [.N]

